OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FClimate change: 'Madness'  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto turn to fossil fuels    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fbecause of Ukraine war     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UN Secretary General says the rush 
OL,6, to use fossil fuels because of the war 
OL,7, in Ukraine is "madness" and threatens  
OL,8, global climate targets.                
OL,10,FThe invasion of Ukraine has seen rapid 
OL,11,Frises in the prices of coal, oil and   
OL,12,Fgas as countries scramble to replace   
OL,13,FRussian sources.                       
OL,15,FBut Antonio Guterres warns that these  
OL,16,Fshort-term measures might "close the   
OL,17,Fwindow" on the Paris climate goals.    
OL,19,FHe also calls on countries, including  
OL,20,FChina, to fully phase out coal by 2040.
